  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
