    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in 700ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [900ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
