          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomato has softened, add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong>,<strong> spicy stock</strong> and <strong>quinoa</strong> to the pan and cook for 15-20 min or until the sweet potato is tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
